interpretation: The "green salad" card represents a time of nourishment and health. This card suggests that you are in a phase of your life where you are taking care of yourself, both physically and mentally. It's a time to prioritize your well-being and make choices that will benefit your health. This card can also suggest a need for balance in your life, as the variety of ingredients in a salad symbolize the need for diversity and moderation. Remember to take care of yourself in all aspects, not just one.
